{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Non-Profit</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #c0392b;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e74c3c 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 36px;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #c0392b;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .mission, .programs, .contact {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .mission p, .programs ul, .contact p {\n            text-align: justify;\n        }\n        .programs ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .programs ul li {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .programs ul li::before {\n            content: '\\2022';\n            color: #c0392b;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 1em;\n            margin-left: -1em;\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #c0392b;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            color: #e74c3c;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Our Community Initiative</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"main-content\">\n        <section class=\"mission\">\n            <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>We are dedicated to fostering a stronger, more vibrant community by providing essential resources and opportunities for all residents. Our goal is to empower individuals and families, creating a supportive network that promotes well-being and sustainable growth.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"programs\">\n            <h2>What We Do</h2>\n            <p>Our programs focus on key areas to address community needs:</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Youth Development: After-school tutoring and mentorship programs.</li>\n                <li>Food Security: Community gardens and food distribution services.</li>\n                <li>Skill Building: Workshops for job training and personal development.</li>\n                <li>Health & Wellness: Access to health resources and educational sessions.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get Involved</h2>\n            <p>Your support makes a difference. Whether through volunteering your time, making a donation, or simply spreading the word, you can help us achieve our mission. Visit our website or contact us to learn more about how you can contribute to our community.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@communityinitiative.org\">info@communityinitiative.org</a></p>\n            <p>Website: <a href=\"#\">www.communityinitiative.org</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Our Community Initiative. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}